## **Step 3 — Use GitHub Copilot or any AI as an *educational assistant***

This is the key safety principle:

**AI is not your lawyer — it is your tutor.**

Inside GitHub or VS Code, you can type:

- **“Explain this repository.”**
- **“Map the structure of the People’s Law School.”**
- **“Show me the LC modules.”**
- **“Help me understand this template.”**

This keeps everything in the realm of **education**, not representation.

